{"tid":801794,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"免費學結他","createTime":"2018-09-01T03:09:38.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-01T11:44:08.000Z","uid":118240,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fa0ff601900e04c4ba0d4b448ee3ca5750ee04e0","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:09:38.000Z","msg":"之前開個幾個一樣嘅 post，之後會習中呢個 post<br />\n<br />\n戴定頭盔先，由於我講明免費，所以唔涉及乜野商業野 <br />\n<br />\n我本身係音樂教育 degree holder，係全職 freelance musician，都做左好多年，唔係掃兩下chord 就話自己識彈出黎教果種。 <br />\n<br />\n教左一段時間，發現最有 passion 學但又最冇能力學既係在職貧窮既人（即是大多數巴絲打既年紀） <br />\n所以希望可以幫到吓大家 <br />\n<br />\n有幾個要求： <br />\n<br />\n只教四堂免費，每堂 30-45 min，要於 4 星期內完成，無得補堂<br />\n<br />\n時間地點要就我，我 studio 係葵興地鐵站行大約 5min 既地方<br />\n我仲有多個地方係炮台山同太子。但呢三個地方唔做得免費同埋時間學費都同我私人收費有少少唔同，詳情私下傾<br />\n<br />\n唔包括我本身既學生 <br />\n<br />\n我都係在職貧窮 JJ，音樂人都要食飯，同埋我本身都有一堆收錢既學生。所以為左唔做爛市保障同行，我只收兩個人免費，過左果四堂後我會再收下 round ，同埋我唔係度公開我真正收費，呢點私下傾<br />\n<br />\n當然可以付費學<br />\n<br />\n呢四堂只係想教到你可以有咁上下既理解能力去自學落去，for beginner 為主 <br />\n當然結果你有興趣，我好鼓勵你繼續學落去。<br />\n<br />\n如果你冇結他但想學我有方法買到平野，呢點都係私下傾 <br />\n<br />\n有意請 add <a href=\"http://t.me/musicmanctc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmusicmanctc&d=cHFr5T%2F05JVuldNlAwFIBcn%2FdpYTMnF8ODxps2tmzCA%3D&h=fdcb4f92\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/musicmanctc</a>"},{"pid":"7a69d441272d3d72a1a3dbbdad09d449f3256f2e","tid":801794,"uid":4302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T03:35:49.000Z","msg":"G 持"},{"pid":"a902bdc8eb583af680a1139f1c0be2396e90539b","tid":801794,"uid":202464,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-01T05:25:03.000Z","msg":"其實即係「免費試鐘」？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n高招，避開畀連登仔攻擊你利用連登搵食。"},{"pid":"4ebc6f6bd1df756341d8b83112ba9489d99dda4a","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-18T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"再收生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a26e14699733941fd575a19ce3ad155a3bd725a","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T04:03:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0a25aa19c3bf50304f7415ead09b7377470adf4","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T11:09:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cbf0b5173944c5902b963b46af2fe9a102ffe045","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-19T15:21:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4068d592858398abe7130dac68e1de0d60a04831","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T10:47:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae77d626074b715ad341e2c316037b69a11c742","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T14:29:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a7df4ff2a579bc61734bcbdc28256e668b31d9","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T17:32:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f26968acc87cead85c735c73b8d8308d8e5b647","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-30T14:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4420d8221682a1e1fbce285dc242c1903a06d334","tid":801794,"uid":118240,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T11:44:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}